name: UFGVehicleDestroyableInterface
comment:
For blueprint support of the interface, we will never add anything to it, just use it to
have a UCLASS to be able to access

name: IFGVehicleDestroyableInterface
comment: Actors attached that implement this interface can be destroyed by a vehicle running over it.

methods.name: GetForceThreshold
methods.comment: @returns the force required (if any) to destroy this object

methods.name: GetDestroyAudioEvent
methods.comment: Audio event to be posted when destroyed

methods.name: GetDestroyEffect
methods.comment: Particle System to be played when destroyed
